uk.ac.kent

Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.kent.Database

  • public final class Database
extends Object
    For details about the API see Hibernate Quick Start .

    Each BaseController stores a reference to this Database and executes Query on it.

    The result of those is transferred to the GUI.

    Author:
    norbert

      • populate

        public void populate()
        Fill the database. Creating a Manager will create a bunch of employees and assign them to this Manager. Creating an Employee causes all relevant records to be created (although the data is fake). This includes PersonalDetailsRecord and EmploymentDetailsRecord.
